    1.

   The 15th Anniversary Edition of The International London Tattoo
   Convention, the most exciting, anticipated and resoundingly successful
   celebration of body art in the world, has been confirmed for the
   weekend of 27/28/29th September 2019 at Tobacco Dock.
   STOP PRESS: Burlesque, Fire Performance & Sword Swallowers just
   announced!
   Entertainment News London Tattoo Convention

STOP PRESS: Burlesque, Fire Performance & Sword Swallowers just announced!

   Wednesday 25 September 2019
   We're thrilled to announce performances from Cervena Fox, Rachel Atlas
   and Marie Devilreux live on the Tattoo Competition stage each day of
   the convention. Come down to the South Vaults to see fire breathing,
   sword swallowing, burlesque and more!
   Doc Price - The Grand Old Man of Ink
