   The Vans Ramp Jam at The London Tattoo Convention
   News London Tattoo Convention

The Vans Ramp Jam at The London Tattoo Convention

   Friday 6 September 2019
   We're excited to be teaming up with Vans at this year's London Tattoo
   Convention, bringing you our first ever weekend Ramp Jam: featuring
   skate demos from Vans Europe pro riders on our brand new half pipe,
   DJ's, giveaways and more...

   Next

   Welcome to the 15th International London Tattoo Convention. We’re
   excited to be back at the iconic Tobacco Dock for Europe's biggest
   celebration of tattoo art and culture.

   The 15th London Tattoo Convention, 27th-28th-29th September 2019,
   promises to be the greatest yet with over 400+ international tattoo
   artists, art exhibitions, fire performers, entertainment, live music,
   street food, craft beer and so much more!

   This year the London Tattoo Convention is truly going to be an event to
   remember.

   Check out our blog to keep up to date with the latest announcements.

   Advance Tickets available now at www.kingpintickets.com

